## Token categories (align with Figma Variables)

Use these categories when defining or consuming tokens. Prefer tokens over raw values everywhere.

| Category | Use for | Example usage |
|----------|--------|----------------|
| **Color** | Backgrounds, borders, text, icons, semantic (success/error/warning) | `var(--color-primary)` or theme `colors.primary` |
| **Typography** | Font family, size, weight, line-height, letter-spacing | `var(--font-body)` or theme `typography.body` |
| **Spacing** | Padding, margin, gaps (use scale, not arbitrary px) | `var(--space-4)` or theme `spacing[4]` |
| **Radius** | Border radius for buttons, cards, inputs | `var(--radius-md)` or theme `radius.md` |
| **Shadow** | Elevation, cards, modals | `var(--shadow-sm)` or theme `shadows.sm` |
| **Breakpoints / Layout** | Grid, container width, responsive behavior | Map to Tailwind/CSS breakpoints if used |

